      <h1>About Pupster</h1>
      <hr>
      <p>Pupster is a searchable online database and resource that helps match rescue dogs to potential adopters by taking a 1 minute quiz, or browsing local dogs for adoption in their area. As of right now, Oregon is the available search area but we plan to expand nationwide. Pupster allows its users to find their perfect match, browse adoptable dogs and rescues to be able to find adopters and foster homes for dogs in need. Pupster has created a unique quiz and algorithm that matches potential adopters to a dog in the database by answering a handful of questions to help you find your match. Why wait? <a href="/adopters">Find your perfect pup today!</a></p>
      <hr>


      <div class="container">
